    <h2> About Us</h2>
     <p>System is about creating event plan with catering detail. System for the customer who want to plan their event by them as per requirement. System that provide the service provider. A system where service provider can come and provide their services and other detail to work with system.</p>
    <p>The main benefit over here is that customer can get more choices of service providers and their services for their event and they can able to get more benefit and better choice. Here the customer have to choose the services that are provided by service provider according to their budget. On the initial state the customer has to enter the budget he/she is willing to spend. Than he has to choose according to it. After the selection of services the customer will get the SMS & Email notifications.</p>
    <p>A main purpose of the system is to allow service provider and caterer to come in to system and provide their detail of services that they provide to get more business out of it. Purpose to provide a platform the customer to plan their own event by themselves and get better choice out of number of service providers.</p>
